28:{"id":"repo-rate","categoryId":"inflation","title":"SARB Policy Rate (Repo Rate)","value":"6.75%","rawValue":6.75,"unit":"%","change":0,"changeLabel":"held at March 2026 MPC","trend":"stable","description":"The SARB held the repo rate at 6.75% at the March 2026 MPC meeting — the second consecutive hold. The decision was unanimous. The MPC cited the Iran war-related oil price shock as creating upside inflation risk. The prime lending rate remains at 10.25%. The SARB's new inflation target is 3% (±1pp), adopted November 2025.","source":"$29","lastUpdated":"2026-03-26","series":"$2a"}
